p></td></tr></tbody></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="padding-left:40px;padding-right:40px;padding-top:8px;padding-bottom:12px"><tbody><tr><td><h1 style="font-size:22px;font-family:&quot;Cormorant Garamond&quot;,&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif;color:#2C2926;margin:0;margin-bottom:6px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-0.005em">Project Update</h1><p style="font-size:13px;line-height:24px;color:#8A8478;margin:0;margin-bottom:24px;letter-spacing:0.04em;margin-top:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">Kimball Residence<!-- --> <!-- -->·<!-- --> <!-- -->April 27, 2026</p><p style="font-size:15px;line-height:28px;color:#4A4540;margin:0;margin-bottom:14px;margin-top:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">Hi Sarah,</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="padding-left:40px;padding-right:40px;padding-top:8px;padding-bottom:12px"><tbody><tr><td><p style="font-size:15px;line-height:28px;color:#4A4540;margin:0;margin-bottom:14px;margin-top:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">Construction kicked off two weeks ago and the site is in good rhythm.</p><p style="font-size:15px;line-height:28px;color:#4A4540;margin:0;margin-bottom:14px;margin-top:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">The new fabric samples landed Friday — the <a href="https://lasprezz.com/portal/projects/kimball" style="color:#4A4540;text-decoration-line:none;text-decoration:underline" target="_blank">Schumacher</a> reads even better in person than on the board, and I&#x27;d love your eyes on it before we lock the order.</p><p style="font-size:15px;line-height:28px;color:#4A4540;margin:0;margin-bottom:14px;margin-top:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">One thing on your plate this week: the floor plan needs your approval by <strong style="font-weight:600;color:#2C2926">May 9</strong> to keep the trades on schedule. Everything else is moving.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="padding-left:40px;padding-right:40px;padding-bottom:24px"><tbody><tr><td><p style="font-size:10px;line-height:24px;letter-spacing:0.14em;color:#8A8478;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:600;margin:0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-top:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">Milestones</p><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="border-bottom:0.5px solid #E8DDD0;padding-top:12px;padding-bottom:12px;vertical-align:middle"><tbody style="width:100%"><tr style="width:100%"><td data-id="__react-email-column" style="vertical-align:middle"><span style="display:inline-block;width:7px;height:7px;margin-right:12px;vertical-align:middle;box-sizing:border-box;background-color:#D4C9BC"></span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#8A8478;text-decoration:line-through">Design intake</span><span style="font-size:11px;color:#8A8478;margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.06em;text-transform:uppercase">Complete</span></td><td align="left" data-id="__react-email-column" style="vertical-align:middle"><span style="font-size:13px;color:#8A8478;letter-spacing:0.02em">Feb 27</span></td></tr></tbody></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="border-bottom:0.5px solid #E8DDD0;padding-top:12px;padding-bottom:12px;vertical-align:middle"><tbody style="width:100%"><tr style="width:100%"><td data-id="__react-email-column" style="vertical-align:middle"><span style="display:inline-block;width:7px;height:7px;margin-right:12px;vertical-align:middle;box-sizing:border-box;background-color:#D4C9BC"></span><span style="font-size:14px;color:#8A8478;text-decoration:line-through">Construction kickoff</span><span style="font-size:11px;color:#8A8478;margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.06em;text-transform:uppercase">Complete</span></td><td align="left" data-id="__react-email-column" style="vertical-align:middle"><sp